### Get lot movement history
GET {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/stockmovements/lot/1

### Post a stock receipt from supplier
POST {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/stockmovements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lotId": 1,
  "quantity": 100,
  "type": 0,
  "transactionDate": "2026-06-23T00:00:00Z",
  "releasedByUserId": 1,
  "jobReference": null,
  "fromLocationId": null,
  "toLocationId": null
}

### Post an issuance to production
POST {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/stockmovements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lotId": 1,
  "quantity": 50,
  "type": 3,
  "transactionDate": "2026-06-23T00:00:00Z",
  "releasedByUserId": 1,
  "jobReference": "JOB-2024-042",
  "fromLocationId": null,
  "toLocationId": null
}

### Try to over-issue (should fail)
POST {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/stockmovements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lotId": 1,
  "quantity": 99999,
  "type": 3,
  "transactionDate": "2026-06-23T00:00:00Z",
  "releasedByUserId": 1,
  "jobReference": "JOB-2024-099",
  "fromLocationId": null,
  "toLocationId": null
}

### Try zero quantity (should fail)
POST {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/stockmovements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lotId": 1,
  "quantity": 0,
  "type": 3,
  "transactionDate": "2026-06-23T00:00:00Z",
  "releasedByUserId": 1,
  "jobReference": "JOB-2024-099",
  "fromLocationId": null,
  "toLocationId": null
}

### Try inactive/nonexistent lot (should fail)
POST {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/stockmovements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lotId": 9999,
  "quantity": 10,
  "type": 3,
  "transactionDate": "2026-06-23T00:00:00Z",
  "releasedByUserId": 1,
  "jobReference": "JOB-2024-099",
  "fromLocationId": null,
  "toLocationId": null
}